00:36.244 --> 00:38.747
{\an8}Captioning Provided By:
MTV NETWORKS

00:38.830 --> 00:44.043
[♪...]

00:46.212 --> 00:48.465
Mom: OK, I NEED
A TOFU SCRAMBLE ON SIX...

00:48.548 --> 00:49.424
Ben: MOM, MOM?

00:49.507 --> 00:51.509
Mom: A B.L.T. ON SEVEN,
HOLD THE MAYO.

00:51.593 --> 00:53.094
OH, I'M SORRY, I'M OUT OF
VEGAN SHORT STACKS.

00:53.178 --> 00:54.637
OOH, AND I OWE YOU
A SIDE OF SLAW.

00:54.721 --> 00:56.973
MOM, MOM, MOM?

00:57.056 --> 00:59.225
{\an1}MOM...

00:59.309 --> 01:01.811
I'M A LITTLE BUSY
RIGHT NOW, BEN.

01:01.895 --> 01:05.522
BUT MOM, I'M STARTING TO
GET HUNGRY.

01:05.607 --> 01:07.233
MY STOMACH IS ABOUT TO GROWL.

01:07.317 --> 01:08.276
[GROWLS]

01:08.359 --> 01:11.029
{\an1}BEN, PLEASE, YOU GOTTA
GIVE ME A BREAK, SWEETIE.

01:11.112 --> 01:12.322
TWO MORE MINUTES.

01:12.405 --> 01:13.323
Ben: MOM...

01:13.406 --> 01:17.702
{\an1}[GROANS]

01:17.786 --> 01:20.955
OK, ALL RIGHT, BEN- BESSIE...

01:21.039 --> 01:23.166
{\an1}OH, NO, NO, I'LL WAIT,
I'LL BE QUIET.

01:23.249 --> 01:24.542
{\an3}BESSIE, CAN YOU PLEASE
MAKE YOUR BROTHER LUNCH?

01:24.626 --> 01:25.835
{\an1}I'M ON IT.

01:25.919 --> 01:28.171
NO, I DON'T WANT HER
TO TOUCH MY FOOD.

01:28.254 --> 01:29.798
I'M NOT EVEN HUNGRY ANYMORE.

01:29.881 --> 01:30.548
I THINK IT WAS
JUST GAS, PROBABLY.

01:30.632 --> 01:32.801
Bessie: EASY, BEN.

01:32.884 --> 01:34.719
{\an1}I'VE GOT YOUR SPECIAL PLATE
RIGHT HERE.

01:34.803 --> 01:37.347
NONE OF THE FOODS
ARE GONNA TOUCH.

01:37.430 --> 01:40.016
{\an3}[WHIMPERS]

01:40.099 --> 01:42.185
DON'T LET THEM TOUCH.

01:42.268 --> 01:43.561
AND WATCH YOUR FINGERS.

01:43.645 --> 01:44.896
{\an3}FINGERS...

01:44.979 --> 01:49.818
BEN, I'VE GOT IT, I'VE SEEN MOM
DO THIS ABOUT A BAJILLION TIMES.

01:49.901 --> 01:53.196
AND FOR THE FINISHING TOUCH...

01:53.279 --> 01:54.322
[GROANING]

01:57.909 --> 01:59.619
[WHIMPERING]

01:59.702 --> 02:02.497
[STAMMERING]

02:02.580 --> 02:04.290
BREATHE, USE YOUR WORDS.

02:04.374 --> 02:05.542
{\an3}SEND ME A MESSAGE
WITH YOUR WORDS, BEN.

02:05.625 --> 02:07.001
{\an3}MAKE WORDS.

02:07.085 --> 02:09.461
MASHED POTATOES IS A FOOD...

02:09.545 --> 02:12.549
AND FOOD CAN'T TOUCH FOOD!

02:12.632 --> 02:15.468
{\an3}OH, GOSH,
ENOUGH IS ENOUGH, BENJAMIN.

02:15.552 --> 02:17.178
YOU ARE SIX YEARS OLD.

02:17.262 --> 02:20.723
ARE YOU GONNA LIVE IN FEAR
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

02:21.683 --> 02:23.101
[SCREAMS]

02:23.184 --> 02:26.521
{\an5}GET IT OFF OF ME,
GET IT OFF OF ME,
GET IT OFF OF ME,
GET IT OFF OF ME.

02:26.604 --> 02:29.524
{\an3}[SIGHS]

02:29.607 --> 02:31.609
{\an3}LET'S GET YOU SOME
PROFESSIONAL HELP, BUDDY.

02:32.861 --> 02:33.528
MM-HMM.

02:33.611 --> 02:37.657
MM-HMM, MM-HMM...

02:37.740 --> 02:39.450
YOU'VE BEEN "MM-HMM-ING"
FOR THE LAST 20 MINUTES

02:39.534 --> 02:40.618
ARE YOU GONNA SAY ANYTHING?

02:40.702 --> 02:42.787
MM-HMM.

02:42.871 --> 02:47.292
MM-HMM, MM-HMM.

02:47.375 --> 02:49.669
MM-HMM, MM-HMM.

02:49.752 --> 02:50.712
SUBJECT...

02:50.795 --> 02:54.299
EXHIBITING... RAGE.

02:55.216 --> 03:00.388
{\an1}NOW, BENJAMIN, WHEN
YOUR CORN FINDS ITS WAY

03:00.471 --> 03:03.349
INTO YOUR MASHED POTATOES...

03:03.433 --> 03:05.351
HOW DOES THAT MAKE YOU FEEL?

03:05.435 --> 03:06.436
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

03:06.519 --> 03:10.982
GROSSED-OUT, SICK, ANGRY,
CONFUSED, OUT OF CONTROL.

03:11.065 --> 03:12.066
[STOMACH GROWLS]

03:12.150 --> 03:13.026
HUNGRY.

03:13.109 --> 03:14.861
OK, THIS IS GOOD.

03:14.944 --> 03:16.446
THIS IS GOOD, YOU'RE DOING
REALLY GREAT WORK HERE.

03:16.529 --> 03:20.491
OK, BENJAMIN, NOW I'M GONNA
SHOW YOU SOME PICTURES

03:20.575 --> 03:22.619
AND YOU JUST TELL ME
WHAT YOU SEE.

03:22.702 --> 03:25.580
[BEN GROANS]

03:25.663 --> 03:27.707
STEAK, ASPARAGUS AND POTATOES.

03:27.790 --> 03:29.500
WRONG.

03:29.584 --> 03:31.628
I SEE A JAZZ TRIO,
BUT THIS ISN'T ABOUT ME.

03:31.711 --> 03:33.963
OK, TRY THIS CARD.

03:34.047 --> 03:35.924
THIS IS STUPID.

03:36.007 --> 03:37.759
I'M GONNA GO
UNWRAP A CHEESE SINGLE.

03:37.842 --> 03:40.345
SUBJECT... LEAVING.

03:40.428 --> 03:42.180
[SIGHS]

03:42.263 --> 03:46.184
CRAZY... EXCLAMATION POINT,
QUESTION MARK.

03:51.940 --> 03:53.191
{\an3}BEN?

03:53.274 --> 03:55.360
{\an3}BEN, BEN...

03:55.443 --> 03:57.111
{\an3}BEN...

03:57.195 --> 03:59.155
{\an3}BEN.

03:59.238 --> 04:01.991
I AM ENTERING YOUR MIND...

04:02.075 --> 04:06.454
OPEN YOUR MIND AND LET ME IN...

04:06.537 --> 04:09.666
COME ON, UNLOCK THE DOOR, BEN...

04:09.749 --> 04:12.835
YOU ARE LETTING ME
INTO YOUR MIND...

04:12.919 --> 04:16.673
{\an6}DON'T WORRY, I'M TAKING OFF
MY SHOES BEFORE I GO
INTO YOUR MIND...

04:16.755 --> 04:18.173
I'M IN YOUR MIND, BEN...

04:18.257 --> 04:22.845
THANK YOU FOR LETTING ME IN
YOUR MIND...

04:22.929 --> 04:24.013
FOOD ISSUES.

04:24.097 --> 04:25.932
[SIGHS] AH, OK, WOW.

04:26.015 --> 04:27.475
[DOOR OPENS]

04:29.060 --> 04:30.603
SURPRISINGLY ORGANIZED IN HERE.

04:30.687 --> 04:32.772
HMM...

04:32.855 --> 04:33.523
WHAT'S THIS HERE?

04:33.606 --> 04:36.359
OH, THESE ARE... INTERESTING.

04:36.442 --> 04:37.568
THE FILE CABINET.

04:37.652 --> 04:40.071
"MEMORIES, SIX TO 12," OK.

04:43.783 --> 04:45.034
NICE WORK, FINGER.

04:47.245 --> 04:47.704
[GASPS]

04:47.787 --> 04:49.539
[GURGLES]

04:49.622 --> 04:51.624
WHOA.

04:51.708 --> 04:55.336
{\an3}HERE COMES
THE SOLAR-POWERED GLIDER...

04:55.420 --> 04:58.506
EIGHT MONTHS, NO PROBLEM THERE.

04:58.589 --> 05:02.218
FIRST BIRTHDAY...

05:02.301 --> 05:04.929
SUBJECT APPEARS TO BE
WELL-ADJUSTED.

05:05.013 --> 05:09.892
{\an1}CHUGGA-CHUGGA, CHUGGA-CHUGGA,
CHUGGA-CHUGGA, CHOO-CHOO.

05:09.976 --> 05:11.769
{\an1}WHOO- OH.

05:11.853 --> 05:14.605
ONE SEC', SWEETIE.

05:14.689 --> 05:16.441
[PHONE RINGS]

05:18.151 --> 05:18.776
{\an1}EAT IT, EAT IT,
EAT IT, EAT IT...

05:18.860 --> 05:21.404
[GASPS]

05:21.487 --> 05:23.197
OH, FINGER, OF COURSE.

05:23.281 --> 05:25.742
HOW DID I NOT REALIZE
THAT THIS IS ALL ABOUT ME?

05:25.825 --> 05:27.076
I'M BEN'S ISSUE.

05:27.160 --> 05:32.707
OH, AS HIS SISTER/PSYCHOLOGIST,
I FEEL TERRIBLE ABOUT THIS.

05:32.790 --> 05:35.251
{\an5}[SIGHS] I HAVE TO SAVE HIM
FROM HIS NEUROSES BEFORE
IT'S TOO LATE

05:35.334 --> 05:37.420
AND HE TURNS INTO
A PERMANENT WEIRDO.

05:37.503 --> 05:37.920
[SNAPPING]

05:38.004 --> 05:40.423
COME ON, FINGER.

05:40.506 --> 05:41.924
{\an3}THESE THINGS WERE
WORKING A MINUTE AGO.

05:42.008 --> 05:44.552
UGH, HEY.

05:44.635 --> 05:45.303
GOOD NEWS, BEN.

05:45.386 --> 05:46.971
TURNS OUT <i> I'M</i> YOUR PROBLEM.

05:47.055 --> 05:48.181
NO DUH.

05:48.264 --> 05:50.600
{\an3}YEAH, SO I TRAVELED INTO
YOUR SUBCONSCIOUS

05:50.683 --> 05:52.852
AND UNRAVELED YOUR DEEP-SEATED
NEGATIVE ASSOCIATION WITH FOOD.

05:52.935 --> 05:53.853
SO ALL YOU NEED...

05:53.936 --> 05:56.105
IT'S NOT NEGATIVE!

05:56.189 --> 05:58.399
I JUST DON'T LIKE
WHEN IT TOUCHES.

05:58.483 --> 05:59.817
{\an3}LAY OFF.

05:59.901 --> 06:02.445
DENIAL.

06:02.528 --> 06:02.820
SEE IT ALL THE TIME.

06:02.904 --> 06:05.865
[CRIES]

06:05.948 --> 06:07.033
[CANNED LAUGHTER]

06:07.116 --> 06:11.204
[LAUGHING]

06:11.287 --> 06:12.455
THAT'S A GOOD ONE.

06:12.538 --> 06:15.041
OK, HAPPY, SO HERE'S
WHAT YOU'RE GONNA DO.

06:15.124 --> 06:17.085
{\an3}GO UP TO BEN,
BUT NOT SO HE CAN SEE YOU

06:17.168 --> 06:19.253
{\an3}AND THEN TICKLE THE BOTTOM
OF HIS FOOT VERY LIGHTLY

06:19.337 --> 06:20.838
BUT NOT TOO LIGHTLY.

06:20.922 --> 06:22.632
{\an3}THEN WHEN HE OPENS HIS MOUTH
FROM THE TICKLE

06:22.715 --> 06:25.802
YOU WHISTLE, SIGNALING ME
TO RELEASE THE CATAPULT.

06:30.431 --> 06:31.474
[GASPS]

06:31.557 --> 06:33.101
[WHISTLES]

06:33.184 --> 06:36.562
Bessie: INCOMING...

06:36.646 --> 06:39.607
[CANNED LAUGHTER]

06:48.241 --> 06:51.702
{\an1}ONE CHOCOLATE MILKSHAKE,
MADE TO ORDER.

06:53.246 --> 06:56.040
WHY IS THERE A T-BONE
FLOATING IN IT?

06:56.124 --> 06:59.127
YOU ALWAYS DO THIS TO ME.

06:59.210 --> 07:01.045
{\an3}[SCREAMS]

06:59.210 --> 07:01.045
{\an1}YIKES.

07:01.129 --> 07:03.840
NOBODY ALWAYS DOES ANYTHING.

07:03.923 --> 07:06.008
IT'S NOT LIKE I'M ALWAYS
FORCING HIM TO...

07:06.092 --> 07:11.139
EAT IT, EAT IT, EAT IT, EAT IT,
EAT IT, EAT IT, EAT IT, EAT IT.

07:11.222 --> 07:13.933
Ben: AH, ALONE AT LAST.

07:14.016 --> 07:16.227
[♪...]

07:16.310 --> 07:18.771
[HUMMING]

07:18.855 --> 07:20.898
AH.

07:20.982 --> 07:23.067
CLEANLINESS FIRST.

07:23.151 --> 07:24.861
HUMMING.

07:30.116 --> 07:33.202
AH, HELLO, OLD FRIEND.

07:35.538 --> 07:35.913
OOH, OOH.

07:35.997 --> 07:37.999
PASTA, PLAIN.

07:38.082 --> 07:40.001
CORN, BUTTERED.

07:40.084 --> 07:42.378
PUDDING, CHOCOLATE.

07:43.796 --> 07:45.089
OH.

07:45.173 --> 07:47.216
Bessie: EVERYTHING MUST GO.

07:47.300 --> 07:49.802
BESSIE'S LIQUIDATION SALE.

07:51.220 --> 07:56.017
{\an5}AND YES, THAT MEANS
THE RAINBOW SUNSHINE GANG
SNOW GLOBE YOU ALWAYS WANTED.

07:56.100 --> 07:58.519
THE ONE WITH GLITTER SNOW?

07:58.603 --> 08:00.188
Bessie: THE ONE
WITH GLITTER SNOW.

08:00.271 --> 08:02.565
THAT ONE EXACTLY.

08:02.648 --> 08:05.526
AND DOORS OPEN IN TWO SECONDS.

08:05.610 --> 08:10.865
NOW IT'S ONE SECOND
AND THE DOORS ARE...

08:10.948 --> 08:12.033
OFFICIALLY OPENED.

08:12.116 --> 08:15.912
[FILM PROJECTOR WHIRS]

08:15.995 --> 08:18.206
[GASPS AND WHIMPERS]

08:18.289 --> 08:22.710
[WHIMPERS AND SQUEALS]

08:22.793 --> 08:25.213
OOH... NO, NO, NO...

08:25.296 --> 08:30.509
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

08:30.593 --> 08:32.385
[GASPING]

08:32.470 --> 08:34.554
I'M GONNA RALPH- OH.

08:34.639 --> 08:36.097
Bessie: THAT'S IT, BEN,
GET IT OUT.

08:36.182 --> 08:38.351
YOU'RE DOING GREAT, BEN.

08:38.433 --> 08:39.936
YOU'RE HALFWAY INTO THE WOODS.

08:40.019 --> 08:43.522
WHICH MEANS YOU'VE BEGUN
YOUR JOURNEY BACK OUT.

08:43.606 --> 08:47.777
{\an5}YOU DON'T HAVE TO
HIDE BEHIND MASHED POTATO WALLS
ANYMORE, BEN.

08:47.860 --> 08:51.072
YOU'RE FORMING POSITIVE,
NEW ASSOCIATIONS

08:51.155 --> 08:53.449
WITH DELICIOUS AND CUDDLY FOODS.

08:53.533 --> 08:55.618
AW, LOOK AT CUPCAKE AND SUSHI.

08:55.701 --> 08:57.161
THEY'RE FRIENDS.

08:57.245 --> 08:58.454
CUPCAKE LOVES SUSHI.

08:58.538 --> 09:00.831
AW, BISCUIT AND STRAWBERRY.

09:00.915 --> 09:03.501
NEXT TO EACH OTHER,
HOLDING HANDS.

09:03.584 --> 09:05.795
WHAT'S THAT, SLICE OF PIZZA?

09:05.878 --> 09:09.173
AW, YOU WANT TO BE NEXT TO
GRILLED CHEESE SANDWICH?

09:09.257 --> 09:11.801
WELL, WHY NOT,
WE'RE ALL THE SAME.

09:11.884 --> 09:14.303
FOOD TOUCHING TOGETHER,
THAT MAKES SENSE.

09:14.387 --> 09:16.138
THERE'S NOTHING
TO BE SCARED ABOUT.

09:16.222 --> 09:18.182
JOIN US, BEN.

09:18.266 --> 09:20.434
GIVE US A HUG, BEN.

09:20.518 --> 09:22.812
WE LOVE YOU, BEN.

09:22.895 --> 09:23.854
COME CLOSER.

09:23.938 --> 09:26.148
NO, NO.

09:26.232 --> 09:27.567
I WON'T DO IT.

09:27.650 --> 09:29.068
YOU FOODS ARE CRAZY,
IT'S NOT NATURAL.

09:29.151 --> 09:32.196
YOU'RE ALMOST THERE.

09:32.280 --> 09:37.535
{\an3}NEW FEELINGS, NEW FEELINGS,
NEW FEELINGS, NEW FEELINGS...

09:37.618 --> 09:39.954
[SCREAMING...]

09:44.333 --> 09:46.961
{\an3}HELLO, BEN,
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

09:47.044 --> 09:49.880
UM, FINE.

09:49.964 --> 09:53.509
FINE?

09:53.592 --> 09:56.053
WITH THE FACT THAT YOU CAN'T
EAT IN A RESTAURANT?

09:56.137 --> 10:00.141
THAT YOU SPEND ALL YOUR
ALLOWANCE ON RUBBER GLOVES?

10:00.224 --> 10:04.020
{\an5}THAT YOU'LL NEVER KNOW THE
PLEASURE OF FRESH STRAWBERRIES
AND ICE CREAM?

10:04.103 --> 10:05.354
NO.

10:05.438 --> 10:09.984
I'M FINE WITH... FOOD TOUCHING.

10:10.067 --> 10:11.694
HUH.

10:11.777 --> 10:13.070
I THINK I'M OVER IT.

10:13.154 --> 10:16.324
HEY, I'M OVER IT, I'M OVER IT.

10:16.407 --> 10:18.576
I'M GLAD TO HEAR IT, BEN.

10:18.659 --> 10:22.455
{\an3}PLUS, THIS PORK CHOP COSTUME
IS REALLY HOT.

10:31.088 --> 10:33.174
HMM, WHAT DO YOU THINK, HAPPY?

10:36.135 --> 10:37.720
YEAH, IT NEEDS
A LITTLE SOMETHING.

10:41.474 --> 10:43.851
[SNIFFS] AH, PERFECTION.

10:43.934 --> 10:47.063
UH, BESSIE, CHECK THIS ONE OUT.

10:47.146 --> 10:49.523
{\an1}TELL ME IF IT'S TOO HEAVY
ON THE CHEDDAR CHUNKS, HUH?

10:49.607 --> 10:51.734
{\an1}PERSONALLY, I THINK THEY
COMPLEMENT THE PEACHES NICELY.

10:51.817 --> 10:54.236
{\an3}UH, NO THANKS, BEN,
I'M GONNA TAKE A RAIN CHECK.

10:54.320 --> 10:55.196
BUT IT SOUNDS DELICIOUS.

10:55.279 --> 10:57.615
OH, DROPPED MY FORK.

10:57.698 --> 10:59.241
{\an1}COME ON.

10:59.325 --> 11:00.409
YOU'LL LOVE IT.

11:00.493 --> 11:02.411
LITTLE CLOSE, BEN, LITTLE CLOSE.

11:02.495 --> 11:05.998
HERE, HERE, I'LL FEED IT TO YOU.

11:06.082 --> 11:07.458
[MOUTHING SILENTLY]

11:07.541 --> 11:10.544
{\an5}FUR TOUCHING SKIN, OK,
FEEL FREE TO BACK OFF
AT ANY TIME, YOU GUYS.

11:10.628 --> 11:14.256
WOW, OK, EVEN CLOSER.
[CHUCKLES WEAKLY]

11:14.340 --> 11:16.509
[GRUNTING] IT'S A LITTLE CLOSE.

11:16.592 --> 11:17.927
I JUST DON'T LIKE
PEOPLE TOO CLOSE.

11:18.010 --> 11:19.387
PEOPLE NEED ROOM... TO BREATHE.

11:19.470 --> 11:21.639
'CAUSE IT'S HARD TO BREATHE.

11:21.722 --> 11:22.014
I NEED AIR.

11:22.098 --> 11:24.308
[GASPS]

11:24.392 --> 11:28.145
{\an1}WHAT, IS SOMEBODY
CLAUSTROPHOBIC?

11:28.229 --> 11:32.108
{\an1}MAYBE YOU NEED
PROFESSIONAL HELP.

11:33.442 --> 11:37.321
[♪...]

11:43.953 --> 11:45.788
Woman: I'M SURE I DON'T HAVE TO
REMIND YOU GIRLS

11:45.871 --> 11:48.791
THAT THE HONEYBEE BEE-ATHLON
IS COMING UP.

11:48.874 --> 11:51.168
{\an3}THIS YEAR, WE DEFEND OUR TITLE
AGAINST THE BEAVERS.

11:51.252 --> 11:52.837
HA, THE BEAVERS.

11:52.920 --> 11:53.671
{\an3}[SCREAMING]

11:53.754 --> 11:55.798
{\an1}WE GOT THIS ONE
IN THE BAG, LADIES.

11:55.881 --> 11:58.134
{\an3}HA, YEAH.

11:58.217 --> 12:00.886
{\an3}THOSE DORKY BEAVERS
CAN ONLY WIN DORK CONTESTS.

12:00.970 --> 12:04.056
DORKS OR NO DORKS, WE DON'T
WANT TO REST ON OUR LAURELS.

12:04.140 --> 12:09.311
{\an5}NOW WE'RE GOING TO START OUT
WITH A PROGRAM OF LIGHT
CALISTHENICS.

12:09.395 --> 12:10.646
{\an5}THEN WE'LL WORK IN
LOW-IMPACT CARDIO.

12:09.395 --> 12:10.646
[DEVICES BEEPING]

12:16.652 --> 12:20.239
{\an5}[GASPS] "RASPBERRY SHORTCAKE
SPACE ATTACK FIVE"
COMES OUT TOMORROW.

12:20.322 --> 12:23.826
AW, MAN, ALL I GOT IS $7.

12:23.909 --> 12:27.580
ALL I'VE GOT IS... $4.10.

12:27.663 --> 12:28.914
LET'S SEE.

12:28.998 --> 12:32.001
I HAVE $4.60 IN MY PIGGY BANK.

12:32.084 --> 12:34.295
$7.50 IN MY SECRET PIGGY BANK.

12:34.378 --> 12:36.797
$1.75, NO, 76 IN MY POCKET.

12:36.881 --> 12:39.341
AND IT'S THE NINTH OF THE MONTH,
SO THERE'S...

12:39.425 --> 12:41.343
APPROXIMATELY $2.17
IN THE COUCH CUSHIONS RIGHT NOW.

12:41.427 --> 12:43.387
STILL NOT ENOUGH.

12:43.471 --> 12:45.848
IF WE ALL PUT OUR MONEY TOGETHER

12:45.931 --> 12:48.350
WE COULD GET "R.S.S.A.V."
THE SECOND IT COMES OUT.

12:48.434 --> 12:51.479
DO YOU MEAN, LIKE, SHARE?

12:51.562 --> 12:53.022
{\an1}I DON'T KNOW,
BETTER THAN WAITING.

12:53.105 --> 12:57.943
GRAB YOUR IRONIC T-SHIRTS
AND YOUR IMAGINARY FRIENDS.

12:58.027 --> 12:59.820
BECAUSE THE FIFTH AND LATEST
EDITION OF THE POPULAR

12:59.904 --> 13:02.865
"RASPBERRY SHORTCAKE
SPACE ATTACK" VIDEO GAME

13:02.948 --> 13:05.451
WILL BE RELEASED TOMORROW
MORNING AT 6:00 A.M. SHARP.

13:05.534 --> 13:09.038
{\an5}DIE-HARD FANS HAVE BEEN
LINING UP TO ENSURE THEY GET
A MUCH-COVETED COPY.

13:09.121 --> 13:10.498
WAIT...

13:10.581 --> 13:12.791
CAN I GET IN WITH YOU GUYS?

13:12.875 --> 13:14.960
YOU CAN HAVE EVERYTHING
IN MY PIGGY BANK.

13:15.044 --> 13:19.215
{\an5}UH, BEN, YOUR PIGGY BANK
IS NEITHER A PIG NOR A BANK,
WHAT'S UP?

13:19.298 --> 13:23.886
{\an5}DUH, I'M NOT GONNA
WALK DOWN THE STREET
HOLDING MY ACTUAL PIGGY BANK.

13:23.969 --> 13:25.387
WE HAVE NO NEED OF YOUR
CONTRIBUTION AT THIS TIME.

13:25.471 --> 13:28.057
COME ON, PLEASE.

13:28.140 --> 13:30.184
BEN, YOU'RE AN AMATEUR.

13:30.267 --> 13:33.395
{\an5}YOU CAN'T EVEN PASS LEVEL TWO ON
"RASPBERRY SHORTCAKE
SPACE ATTACK FOUR."

13:33.479 --> 13:36.106
{\an5}PLUS, YOU GET THE CONTROLLER
ALL STICKY WITH YOUR
APPLE-JUICE MITTS.

13:36.190 --> 13:38.025
I'LL WASH, PLEASE.

13:38.108 --> 13:39.568
OK, BEN.

13:39.652 --> 13:43.906
{\an5}IF YOU LEAVE RIGHT NOW,
WE <i> MIGHT</i> LET YOU TRY IT
FOR, LIKE, A MINUTE.

13:43.989 --> 13:46.659
BUT WE ALSO MIGHT NOT.

13:46.742 --> 13:49.703
I'LL TAKE IT, I'LL TAKE IT.

13:49.787 --> 13:52.831
[SCOFFS] HE IS <i> SO</i> YOUR FAMILY.

13:54.208 --> 13:57.044
{\an1}I AM AN EIGHTH-LEVEL BOSS,
GERM GOBLIN.

13:57.127 --> 13:58.629
MY POWERS INCLUDE
SALMONELLA RAYS...

13:58.712 --> 13:59.255
{\an1}LIGHTNING STRIKES
AND THUNDER SHAKES.

13:59.338 --> 14:02.466
{\an1}[SCREAMS]

14:04.301 --> 14:08.389
UH, ONE PLEASE.

14:08.472 --> 14:11.100
COME ON, COME ON, COME ON,
COME ON, COME ON, COME ON.

14:13.269 --> 14:16.522
HA, PAWED.

14:16.605 --> 14:17.189
AW...

14:17.273 --> 14:18.524
[♪...]

14:18.607 --> 14:21.110
{\an5}YOU GOT IT.

14:18.607 --> 14:21.110
YEAH.

14:21.193 --> 14:22.194
THAT'S MY GIRL.

14:22.278 --> 14:23.529
[BESSIE IMITATES SHOOTING]

14:23.612 --> 14:28.200
[OVERLAPPING CONVERSATION]

14:28.284 --> 14:29.827
YOU LIKE THAT, YOU LIKE THAT?

14:29.910 --> 14:31.453
WELL, HOW ABOUT THIS?

14:31.537 --> 14:34.623
[LAUGHING AND GROWLING]

14:34.707 --> 14:36.333
Bessie: OK, YOU GUYS,
JUST ONE MORE HOUR

14:36.417 --> 14:39.378
AND THEN WE'LL START TRAINING
FOR THE BEE-ATHLON.

14:39.461 --> 14:41.422
{\an5}BESSIE, YOU MISSED DINNER.

14:39.461 --> 14:41.422
{\an3}UH-HUH.

14:41.505 --> 14:44.842
{\an1}DID YOU HEAR WHAT I SAID,
WE HAD PIZZA BAGELS.

14:44.925 --> 14:45.801
{\an3}UH-HUH.

14:45.884 --> 14:47.886
{\an1}CAN I TAKE ALL THE STUFF
IN YOUR ROOM?

14:47.970 --> 14:49.013
{\an3}UH-HUH.

14:49.096 --> 14:50.347
ARE YOU A MONKEY'S GIRLFRIEND?

14:50.431 --> 14:51.348
{\an3}UH-HUH.

14:51.432 --> 14:52.308
{\an1}[LAUGHS]

14:52.391 --> 14:53.350
CAN I PLAY NOW?

14:53.434 --> 14:55.185
WHAT, NO.

14:58.355 --> 14:58.981
BEDTIME.

14:59.064 --> 15:01.442
YOU SET YOUR ALARM TO GO TO BED?

15:01.525 --> 15:04.153
{\an3}OK, SO, UH, WHO GETS TO
TAKE THE GAME HOME?

15:04.236 --> 15:05.988
All: ME, ME, ME.

15:06.071 --> 15:08.866
TECHNICALLY, THE HIVE
ISN'T ANYONE'S HOME, PER SE.

15:08.949 --> 15:12.119
SO, UM, WHY DON'T WE JUST
LEAVE THE GAME HERE?

15:12.202 --> 15:13.829
PFT, NICE TRY, "STINKENBOTTOM."

15:13.912 --> 15:16.498
LIKE WE'RE REALLY GONNA
LET YOU KEEP IT.

15:16.582 --> 15:20.377
{\an5}MY MOM IS THE ONLY ONE
WHO WON'T CHECK ON US
FOR 12 HOURS STRAIGHT.

15:20.461 --> 15:22.296
UH, MESSY'S GOT A POINT.

15:22.379 --> 15:24.798
{\an3}YEAH, HIPPY-MOMMY'S
LOOSE LIKE THAT.

15:24.882 --> 15:28.177
INITIATING BERRY-BLASTERS.

15:28.260 --> 15:32.264
SETTING HOT-FUDGE PHASERS...
FOR MOLTEN.

15:32.348 --> 15:33.307
TELL MY FAMILY I LOVE THEM.

15:33.390 --> 15:35.643
[♪...]

15:35.726 --> 15:39.730
[SCREECHING]

15:42.107 --> 15:44.068
[MONSTERS JABBERING]

15:54.620 --> 15:56.205
[SHRIEKS]

15:57.164 --> 15:58.749
GOT 'EM ALL, HOME BASE.

15:58.832 --> 16:00.000
ROUNDING BACK.

16:00.084 --> 16:01.835
[SCREAMS]

16:04.296 --> 16:06.757
WHOA, I'M HIT, I'M HIT.

16:06.840 --> 16:07.966
SHORTCAKE-ONE TO AIRBASE.

16:08.050 --> 16:09.259
AIRBASE, PLEASE ADVISE.

16:09.343 --> 16:10.928
SEEKING PERMISSION TO LAND,
COME IN, AIRBASE.

16:11.011 --> 16:12.554
I'M GOING DOWN, AIRBASE,
I'M HIT.

16:12.638 --> 16:14.390
I'M GOING DOWN, MAYDAY, MAYDAY,
MAYDAY, MAYDAY, MAYDAY.

16:14.473 --> 16:16.058
[GASPS]

16:16.141 --> 16:17.559
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

16:18.644 --> 16:20.396
[FOOTSTEPS SOUNDING]

16:20.479 --> 16:20.979
SANTA?

16:21.063 --> 16:23.565
BUT IT'S BARELY FALL.

16:23.649 --> 16:26.360
OR IS IT... AN INTRUDER?

16:26.443 --> 16:28.570
{\an5}[GASPS] TRYING TO STEAL
"RASPBERRY SHORTCAKE
SPACE ATTACK FIVE."

16:28.654 --> 16:30.989
ALL RIGHT, CRIMINAL ELEMENT.

16:31.073 --> 16:32.574
GIVE UP PEACEFULLY AND I WILL
SPARE YOU A CITIZEN'S ARREST.

16:32.658 --> 16:35.202
DING-A-LING-A-LING.

16:35.285 --> 16:36.245
{\an1}YOUR ALARM JUST WENT OFF,
BEDTIME, SEE YOU.

16:36.328 --> 16:39.081
UH...

16:39.164 --> 16:41.917
{\an3}OH, HI, BESSIE, YOU WANT SOME
MICROWAVE PIZZA-PADOODLES?

16:42.000 --> 16:45.379
BUT, BEES, WE HAVE TO TRAIN FOR
THE BEE-ATHLON IN THE MORNING.

16:45.462 --> 16:49.800
{\an1}WE SHOULD GET A FULL
EIGHT HOURS REST- I CALL NEXT.

16:49.883 --> 16:52.219
[BEEPING AND BLASTING]

16:55.848 --> 16:57.224
WELL, THIS CAN'T BE RIGHT.

16:57.307 --> 16:59.393
ACCORDING TO YOUR PULSES,
YOU'RE ALL COMATOSE.

16:59.476 --> 17:01.103
[GRUNTS]

17:01.186 --> 17:03.313
GIRLS, I WANT YOU ALL TO RAMP UP
YOUR TRAINING IMMEDIATELY.

17:03.397 --> 17:04.647
JUMP ROPE, TWO MILES DAILY.

17:04.732 --> 17:07.108
BICEP CURLS, 30 REPS.

17:07.192 --> 17:07.776
TRICEP CURLS, 60 REPS.

17:07.859 --> 17:10.445
LUNGES, 50, TRUNKS, 10,000.

17:10.529 --> 17:12.948
MOMMY, OK.

17:13.031 --> 17:15.701
AS IF ANYONE EVER
LOSES TO THE BEAVERS.

17:15.784 --> 17:19.371
{\an1}FLYING A LITTLE TOO CLOSE
TO THE SUN, PORTIA.

17:19.454 --> 17:22.374
[SIGHS] DON'T WORRY,
MRS. GIBBONS, WE'RE ON IT.

17:22.458 --> 17:24.835
TRAINING WILL COMMENCE
<i>AFTER ONE MORE GAME.</i>

17:24.917 --> 17:27.296
[♪...]

17:27.378 --> 17:29.631
{\an1}I HEARD SOMEONE DIE,
IT'S MY TURN NOW, YOU SAID.

17:29.715 --> 17:33.969
{\an5}DOESN'T COUNT,
I HAVE 25 BONUS LIVES
PLUS TWO EXTRA HEART POWER-UPS.

17:34.052 --> 17:36.513
LESS TALKING, MORE LOOKING.

17:36.597 --> 17:38.640
{\an3}YOU WON'T GET A TURN IF YOU
DON'T FIND US MORE CHEAT CODES.

17:38.724 --> 17:43.520
[GROANS] CRUSTY OLD BEES.

17:43.604 --> 17:44.229
AH.

17:46.607 --> 17:49.818
I'VE GOT $23.47.

17:49.902 --> 17:52.654
{\an3}FOR JUST ONE TURN,
ALL THIS COULD BE YOURS.

17:52.738 --> 17:54.490
WEAK, BEAT IT, KID.

17:54.573 --> 17:56.658
HUH, WAS IT, WHO THE, WHAT?

17:56.742 --> 17:58.452
OH, THINGS ARE FLASHING.

17:58.535 --> 18:02.664
{\an6}WAIT, HOW DID THIS, OOPS,
I THINK I JUST ERASED
ALL YOUR EMAILS.

18:02.748 --> 18:05.083
BEE-ATHLON.

18:05.167 --> 18:06.460
THE BEE-ATHLON IS IN
15 MINUTES.

18:06.543 --> 18:08.629
COME ON, BEES, DOUBLE-TIME.

18:08.712 --> 18:11.131
ALL RIGHT, PAUSE IT.

18:13.008 --> 18:15.719
[GRUNTS] I CAN'T MOVE.

18:15.803 --> 18:17.638
MY LEGS WON'T LISTEN TO ME.

18:17.721 --> 18:19.598
WE GOTTA GET TO THE BEE-ATHLON,
JUST, JUST TRY HARDER.

18:19.681 --> 18:23.143
[STRAINING AUDIBLY]

18:23.227 --> 18:28.524
[GRUNTING]

18:28.607 --> 18:31.068
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

18:31.151 --> 18:32.319
{\an1}[GRUNTS]

18:32.402 --> 18:34.363
[GRUNTS]

18:34.446 --> 18:36.281
[ALL GRUNTING]

18:39.618 --> 18:40.202
{\an3}[GRUNTING]

18:40.285 --> 18:42.704
GIRLS, WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

18:42.788 --> 18:44.540
{\an1}THOSE LUMPY BEAVERS ARE
WAITING AT THE STARTING LINE.

18:44.623 --> 18:46.750
{\an3}NOW SCOOT.

18:46.834 --> 18:47.876
HI, BEES.

18:47.960 --> 18:49.837
HE SAID "HI" TO THE GIRLS.

18:49.920 --> 18:51.213
HE, HE LOVES THEM.

18:51.296 --> 18:53.215
LET'S BEAT THOSE DWEEBS ALREADY.

18:53.298 --> 18:54.716
I'M PAUSED ON LEVEL 59.

18:56.134 --> 18:57.010
[CHEERING]

18:57.094 --> 18:58.595
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

18:58.679 --> 19:02.140
[CHEERING...]

19:07.396 --> 19:09.147
[GASPING AND GROANING]

19:15.529 --> 19:16.947
{\an1}[GURGLES]

19:17.906 --> 19:19.908
[INHALES WEAKLY]

19:25.330 --> 19:26.331
[SNORING]

19:26.415 --> 19:29.585
[CHEERING]

19:29.668 --> 19:32.296
[CHANTING]: BEAVERS,
BEAVERS, BEAVERS.

19:32.838 --> 19:36.091
GIRLS, I AM SHOCKED.

19:36.174 --> 19:39.344
AND TO THINK I LENT YOU
MY HAND WEIGHTS.

19:39.428 --> 19:42.681
[GRUNTING]

19:42.764 --> 19:45.934
WE JUST LOST THE BEE-ATHLON
TO THE BEAVERS.

19:46.018 --> 19:47.519
OH, THE SHAME.

19:47.603 --> 19:48.520
[SIGHS]

19:48.604 --> 19:51.023
{\an3}HA, BEES.

19:51.106 --> 19:52.441
HA, CAN WE JOIN YOUR LOSER CLUB?

19:52.524 --> 19:53.650
{\an1}NOT.

19:53.734 --> 19:55.402
HA, 15 MINUTES FROM NOW

19:55.485 --> 19:56.570
EVERYONE WHO READS MY BLOG
WILL KNOW ABOUT THIS.

19:56.653 --> 19:59.156
{\an1}REMATCH.

19:59.239 --> 20:02.868
{\an1}ARTICLE 36, SECTION EIGHT
STATES THAT

20:02.951 --> 20:04.786
ANY TROOP WHOSE PERFORMANCE
WAS AFFECTED BY POOR HEALTH

20:04.870 --> 20:06.371
CAN CALL A REMATCH.

20:06.455 --> 20:09.875
{\an3}YEAH, BUT IT'S UP TO THE
OPPOSING TO ACCEPT YOUR APPEAL.

20:09.958 --> 20:12.669
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN MEMORIZE THE RULEBOOK.

20:12.753 --> 20:14.922
{\an1}[SNORING]

20:15.005 --> 20:16.340
WHAT IF WE SWITCH IT UP?

20:16.423 --> 20:18.800
{\an1}ONE ROUND OF "R.S.S.A.V.,"
WINNER TAKES ALL.

20:18.884 --> 20:21.595
WE'LL TAKE IT.

20:21.678 --> 20:22.095
YOU BEES ARE BANANAS.

20:22.179 --> 20:24.348
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

20:24.431 --> 20:25.265
LET'S NOT GO
THROWING THE "B" WORD AROUND.

20:25.349 --> 20:28.477
DO YOU ACCEPT THE CHALLENGE
OR NOT?

20:28.560 --> 20:31.605
{\an3}WE ACCEPT.

20:31.688 --> 20:36.401
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING...]

20:39.279 --> 20:40.572
Girl: YES.

20:40.656 --> 20:41.323
AUGH, I'M OUT.

20:43.867 --> 20:44.284
I'M OUT.

20:46.662 --> 20:47.663
I'M OUT.

20:49.289 --> 20:50.499
I'M OUT.

20:50.582 --> 20:53.043
Honeybees: BESSIE,
COME ON, BESSIE, YOU GO, GIRL.

20:53.126 --> 20:57.631
YEAH, BESSIE, COME ON, BESSIE,
BESSIE, BESSIE, BESSIE.

20:57.714 --> 21:00.342
COME ON, BESSIE, WE NEED YOU.

21:01.760 --> 21:03.428
[SCREAMS]

21:07.307 --> 21:10.560
{\an5}[CHORUS VOCALIZING...]

21:07.307 --> 21:10.560
[♪...]

21:10.644 --> 21:12.646
{\an1}[GASPING]

21:12.729 --> 21:17.234
{\an5}[CHORUS VOCALIZING]

21:12.729 --> 21:17.234
[♪...]

21:25.117 --> 21:29.413
I'M BREAKING UP,
I'M BREAKING UP.

21:38.046 --> 21:38.714
[GASPING]

21:38.797 --> 21:42.217
BEATEN AT VIDEO GAMES?

21:42.300 --> 21:44.219
{\an1}BY GIRLS?

21:44.302 --> 21:44.803
[DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES]

21:44.886 --> 21:47.014
OH, LIKE, WHOA.

21:47.097 --> 21:49.725
SHE'S GOING BEYOND THE BOSS.

21:49.808 --> 21:51.685
[ROARING]

21:51.768 --> 21:53.729
[GASPING]

21:53.812 --> 21:56.064
WHAT, WHAT?

21:56.148 --> 21:56.690
NO, NO-NO-NO, NO,
I NEED THAT UPGRADE.

21:56.773 --> 21:59.234
[GROANING]

21:59.317 --> 22:00.527
I'M BROKE.

22:00.610 --> 22:01.403
<i>NADA.</i>

22:01.486 --> 22:02.654
I GOT LINT.

22:02.738 --> 22:05.532
Ben: HEY, HOW'S IT GOING
UP HERE?

22:05.615 --> 22:09.077
[GASPS] THERE'S MY
FAVORITE BROTHER.

22:09.161 --> 22:09.911
HAVE YOU BEEN GROWING?

22:09.995 --> 22:11.705
YOU LOOK LIKE A TEENAGER.

22:11.788 --> 22:15.208
LISTEN, HOW WOULD YOU LIKE TO
BUY US THE HIGH-LEVEL UPGRADE

22:15.292 --> 22:16.793
{\an3}IN EXCHANGE FOR
FIVE WHOLE TURNS?

22:16.877 --> 22:19.046
TOO LATE.

22:19.129 --> 22:20.714
I JUST GOT THIS SWEET JETPACK.

22:20.797 --> 22:22.424
[SCREAMING]

22:22.507 --> 22:23.967
Ben: WHOO-HOO.

22:24.051 --> 22:25.719
[HONEYBEES GROAN]

22:25.802 --> 22:31.433
[♪...]

23:06.134 --> 23:11.348
[CHILDREN LAUGHING]
